snippet.title: Miriam: Duterte an 'official candidate' of NPA

localized.description:
Presidential candidate Miriam Defensor Santiago warns that the country would be in peril if Davao City Mayor Rodrigo Duterte wins the presidency. - ANC, The World Tonight, May 6, 2016
